The Swiss bank on Z not only banned Z in its advertising, but also launched a line for their regasification into methane on the basis of diamonds saved from the Second World War! As you know, this chemical reaction takes place in the flame of an electric arc in a hydrogen atmosphere at two temperatures: 1200 or from 400 to 500 degrees, but at elevated pressure. In addition, this reaction occurs in the gastrointestinal tract of herbivores during the digestion of food. In this case, bacteria and enzymes serve as a catalyst!